title: MOTD Live - FA Cup Final 2015 - 30th May 2015 - 720p x264
description:
SPORT: Match of the Day Live - Arsenal v Aston Villa
On: BBC 1 HD   
Date: Saturday 30th May 2015 
Time: 17:15 to 19:50 

From Wembley, Gary Lineker introduces live coverage of the 134th FA Cup final, between Arsenal and Aston Villa. Arsenal are the reigning champions, after winning a thrilling final against Hull last year with an extra-time winner from Aaron Ramsey, and they could lift the trophy for a record twelfth time. Aston Villa have reached their first final for 15 years and they will be hoping to end a 58-year wait for the title. Studio guests include Alan Shearer, Martin Keown and Dion Dublin. Commentary by Guy Mowbray and Danny Murphy.
